<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause"?><clause id="_8815f136-93f1-4149-96db-6d52eb0c4995" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NSW"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>I4D32</sptc><title id="_f806b2ec-bcb3-4ac4-bff5-0c572555f75e">Continental seating: egress doorways</title><archive-num>2019: NSW H101.12.6</archive-num><subclause id="_e95b04ca-5487-4b08-93c4-6208b2d4bdd9" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_7757e950-6e8b-499e-bddd-b5933d3c8042">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Egress doorways through the walls of the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2329_1.0.0.xml#_29badeb5-89c1-45af-a10d-fb25847d52c3" id="_0a4a0c6d-559d-41c0-8954-db6336e95d1b" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">auditorium</xref>—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_223eb778-1dec-4226-be63-0769dab16189">must have an aggregate width of at least twice the sum of the clearances specified in Column 3 of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/6738_0.4.0.xml#_9eec4a78-bd95-4ed4-b5fd-0fdff5779056" id="_1a4345c7-d709-400a-81d8-8a251f066773" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">NSW Table I4D29</xref> for each <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2458_5.1.0.xml#_0d278c41-777a-48f5-8130-efe976c8bf82" id="_41ebe054-0f96-4f3f-b056-7a91ea99d28a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">row</xref> of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2329_1.0.0.xml#_29badeb5-89c1-45af-a10d-fb25847d52c3" id="_f5861d39-a736-47dc-95c9-9d7b115619f0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">auditorium</xref> to be served by those doorways; and</li><li id="_b0a2d9a3-079a-4a50-95a0-b55f8ed21752">must be provided at each end of every fifth <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2458_5.1.0.xml#_0d278c41-777a-48f5-8130-efe976c8bf82" id="_b2b38182-4b5a-4b66-9e60-1987118ff752" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">row</xref>, excluding the first 2 <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2458_5.1.0.xml#_0d278c41-777a-48f5-8130-efe976c8bf82" id="_9ad0794f-2a97-4985-8ebf-32c174d5d307" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">rows</xref> and the last 2 <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2458_5.1.0.xml#_0d278c41-777a-48f5-8130-efe976c8bf82" id="_6e352c76-1674-4808-a6e2-f56d74133b09" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">rows</xref> in the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2329_1.0.0.xml#_29badeb5-89c1-45af-a10d-fb25847d52c3" id="_a6abcc3f-8970-4b02-a076-cb103ba13c4f" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">auditorium</xref> if those <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2458_5.1.0.xml#_0d278c41-777a-48f5-8130-efe976c8bf82" id="_dff7fabe-0113-48e0-a8e6-16571f317753" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">rows</xref> each contain no more than 16 seats; and</li><li id="_7dc3fad9-cc7e-4bf4-b727-6199d109a6a1">must lead—<ol><li id="_79eb2dae-8010-439d-b8ae-bd7ed07671aa">directly to a road or <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1385_0.4.0.xml#_b4a20ca6-0197-4381-9e50-85c757fa574f" id="_c974628e-6dbc-49c2-a4c8-9351a06e81c4" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">open space</xref>; or</li><li>into a foyer or other area giving access to a road or <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1385_0.4.0.xml#_b4a20ca6-0197-4381-9e50-85c757fa574f" id="_7ad769c8-347c-464b-b5bf-fa002c742a14" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">open space</xref>; and</li></ol></li><li id="_e3585d0e-3186-46f5-b3ba-094b774230c3">must be provided with <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_8c71ae5a-95ec-4444-b683-0d29a454cf65" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref> signs if the egress doorways are not sufficiently conspicuous.</li></ol></subclause></clause>